description:
Danny welcomes friend of the show Hannah A. Brown to Everything Iconic to talk about the Wendy Williams Lifetime event, home reno shows, and this week's Real Housewives of Atlanta, which featured crab cake drama and a murder mystery party. They also go on an extensive She's The Man detour.


RHOA Recap: 12:45ish
